data.description: **Assumable VA loan at 2.875%**  Welcome to your new home in the coveted Vail School District! This spacious and well maintained 4 bed, 2 bath home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. This home boasts generously sized bedrooms, providing plenty of room for your family and guests. The open-concept layout ensures that everyone has their own space to relax and enjoy. This home has lots of upgrades to include, quartz countertops, whole home water softener system and solar system ensures you can stay cool in those hot summer months without a high electric bill. The extended 2 car garage providing ample storage space. Solar is currently leased but seller is willing to pay off balance at closing. This home is sure to check all the boxes on your wish list
